Minimal Interface

A minimal Signalforge implementation must support:

ingest(input)
sieve(input) -> invariant_core
stress_test(core) -> fracture_map
repair(fracture_map) -> reinforced_core
convert(reinforced_core) -> leveraged_core
time_lock(leveraged_core) -> stable_core
render(stable_core, medium) -> deployed_artifact
measure(deployed_artifact) -> feedback
reingest(feedback) -> next_iteration


